==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stylo-
<hw>Sty"lo-</hw> <pr>(st⟦imac⟧"l⟦osl⟧-)</pr>. <def>A combining form used
in anatomy to indicate <xex>connection with</xex>, or <xex>relation
to</xex>, <xex>the styloid process of the temporal bone</xex>; <as>as,
<ex>stylo</ex>hyal, <ex>stylo</ex>mastoid,
<ex>stylo</ex>maxillary</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stylobate</ent>⟦br⟧
